item.title: Silabs client wont run?
item.dc:creator: @n0va_k0 n0va k0
item.description:
@n0va_k0 wrote:

You don’t need moparscape 3.2 unless you want to play normal servers without silabs and better connection. I’ll try my best to explain it :l

Just download it and save it to your desktop. It will then look like a rar file. You know like a purple book,blue then green book stacked on each other. Right click it then you will see extract files. Click it and something will pop up called extraction path and options. Click ok then another thing will pop up. Look on top left and it will say extract all or extract files. Click it and it will turn into a normal document. There you go just click that and it will have a few things you can click like silabv5,silabv4, click the one that says silabv5 by server guy
